Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:36.73,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身衣服和你很相称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常性感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的樱井令我燃起了沉睡于心中的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我一直都没察觉到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迷上樱井你了 要和我交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小傻瓜 爱总是突如其来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我甩掉 你可别后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候让橘知道你对他的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这么说哦 响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在向我们搭讪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗 等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的路上有没有遇到老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没遇到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雪糕都化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我想纯一和美也肚子都饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上开始做 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 美也你别插手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次连汤包和茶包都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果做出了味道新奇的味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 谁都会有失误的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么结局嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才去买东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才去买东西的时候在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一到暑假就有那么多情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我买东西的时候也没见到几对情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 可能是我运气好见到很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做很多好吃的 你再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 伸长脖子等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单是看就觉得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这桌菜会不会太贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗此刻正用心做着提神料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓贯注精魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又信以为真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再教你些其他的消暑料理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是练棍料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓「练棍」是广东话练习的「练」和棍棒的「棍」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有雄壮的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是练中国拳法的人都会吃的菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真无邪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也该是小梨穗向橘表明心意的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海之主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能放你这家伙走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐们的大学生活如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是一般 不过看起来挺乐在其中的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 她们还进了网球协会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她们还是很热情地教了我很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的菜式也是学姐们教的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了老哥 食欲总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么满意 我的心血总算没白费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一和美也对我的厨艺这么满意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…下次再来做饭 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃太饱走不动了 老哥你去接啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是找你的 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这里是橘家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我是中多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 可能有点突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果明天有空的话一起去游乐园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然是找美也的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}这样啊 太好了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 不过我一个人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚱蜢面具 这个好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去我去 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小逢也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我要和纱江还有小逢去游乐园玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待 真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品 甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才不是说吃饱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品放另一个胃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗也要吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的另一个胃每次都让我惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小企鹅冰沙 透心凉的冰沙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小企鹅冰沙 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 会不会太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃光的话小心吃坏肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来现在应该是吃着雪糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗 分你一点美也特制的七色冰沙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梨穗 今晚住下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒着这么大雨走的话 回家感冒就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 老哥 这样比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看梨穗子愿不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 那我就留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会留在纯一家过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉今天发生太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要好好表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 小梨穗就用这床被子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你美也 特意为我准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也和你一起睡也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就能枕着软绵绵的胸部睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的衣服合身吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 我的衣服合身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 美也的衣服这里太紧了穿不进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问老哥借是借对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 没什么事的话老哥你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡迷糊了 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 给我醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗手间…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰沙吃太多了吧 你是小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子吗 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一才是 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 还不觉得累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的时候暑假每晚都放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有种带降落伞的烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 确实有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一最喜欢把从天而降的小小降落伞接住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子从以前开始就喜欢线香烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些闪烁的小火花很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来还经常跟你比赛谁烧得久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中的最后一个暑假也快要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢 时间过得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入学典礼就像才刚发生不久的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好毕业后做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子你想好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？我也还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们差不多要下决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从幼儿园开始我们就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后还能继续在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,351)}纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(150,351)}梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都陪在我身边 所以才没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我一直都喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到今天我终于清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望今后也能陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这茶真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为这是玉露茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为是梨穗子泡的所以才好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 因为这是为喜欢的人泡的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…你们两个的脸都很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶太热了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间里太热了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑？一点都不可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不可疑 很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘 下周终于迎来七咲的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 塚原学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毕业之后也能好好相处真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 都是托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有时候不能把自己的内心感情说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还藏着自己真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱既能使人变强但同时也会使人变弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
